CAREER BEST TIMES

Event Time Meet Date Place 50 Free 26.37 CSU Magnus Invitational Nov 21, 2014 67th 100 Free 56.27 CSU Magnus Invitational Nov 23, 2014 53rd 200 Free 1:59.10 2015 Big East Conference Championships Feb 20, 2015 – 500 Free 5:20.88 2015 Big East Conference Championships Feb 19, 2015 – 1000 Free 11:05.95 IUPUI vs. Ball State, Xavier Jan 09, 2015 8th 1650 Free 18:08.03 2015 Big East Conference Championships Feb 21, 2015 – 100 Back 1:00.01 Cleveland State Magnus Cup Nov 21, 2015 22nd 2016 Big East Conference Championships Feb 26, 2016 – 200 Back 2:12.27 Cleveland State Magnus Cup Nov 22, 2015 26th 100 Fly 1:00.32 2017 Big East Conference Championships Feb 23, 2017 – 200 Fly 2:20.00 Xavier vs. Wright State Jan 28, 2017 8th 200 IM 2:13.05 Cleveland State Magnus Cup Nov 20, 2015 28th 400 IM 4:40.95 2016 Big East Conference Championships Feb 26, 2016

2016-17: Set a personal best time of 1:00.32 in a time trial for the 100 fly at BIG EAST Championships... Set a time of 2:20.00 in the 200 fly during meet against Wright State...Set a season-best time of 1:00.25 in the 100 back at the 2017 BIG EAST Championships...Also competed in the 200 back and 400 IM at the conference championships.

2015-16: Qualified for BIG EAST Championships in three events...Competed in the 400 IM and 100 back at the conference championship... Posted a career-best time of 4:40.95 in the 400 IM at the BIG EAST Championships...Matched her career best time of 1:00.01 in the 100 back at the conference championship...Also met the BIG EAST qualifiying standard and set her Xavier-career best tin the 200 IM at CSU Magnus Cup.

2014-15: Set the 20th fastest time in school history in the 1650 free at CSU Magnus (18:12.87) … Posted a time of 2:19.83 in the 200 IM against Cumberland.

Prior to Xavier: Was All-Ohio four times while at Rutherford B. Hayes ... Named First Team All-OCC four times ... hold five school records ... Seven time conference champion ... five time sectional champion ... High school team went undefeated in 2012 ... was named team MVP as a senior.

Personal: Born Aug. 19, 1996 in Danville, Ky. ... daughter of Michael DeWitt and Brenda Shaw DeWitt ... father played basketball at Ohio Wesleyan ... mother was a swimmer at Wittenberg ... undecided on a major.
